<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #e0f7fa; 
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #0288d1; 
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center; /* Center align header text */
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.8rem; /* Slightly smaller font size */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 400px; /* Set a max width for the container */
            margin: 20px auto; /* Center container horizontally */
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff; /* White background for content */
            border-radius: 8px; /* Rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Subtle shadow */
        }

        .container p {
            font-size: 0.8rem; /* Smaller font size */
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-align: left; /* Align text to the right */
        }

        .container .greeting {
            font-size: 1rem; /* Smaller font size for greeting */
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        footer {
            max-width: 400px;
            background-color: #0288d1; /* Same dark blue as header */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center; /* Center align footer text */
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.8rem; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Duel</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <p class="greeting">Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
        <p>We are thrilled to have you with us. Welcome to Duel, where we strive to bring you the best.</p>
        <p>Feel free to explore and reach out if you need any assistance.</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Duel. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
